headlines.description: — Jack Podlesny kicked a 53-yard field goal with three seconds remaining, and No. 11 Georgia handed No. 6 Cincinnati its only loss of the season with a dramatic 24-21 victory in the Peach Bowl on Friday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Podlesny's FG lifts Georgia past Cincinnati in Peach Bowl
